item.title: Kodo citata ir paveikslėlis
Home Page
item.description: He decided water-skiing on a frozen lake wasn’t a good idea. In that instant, everything changed. The beauty of the sunset was obscured by the industrial cranes. The Guinea fowl flies through the air with all the grace of a turtle. The blue parrot drove by the hitchhiking mongoose.
